  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $(x_n)$ be a real sequence.\n- [label=(\\alph*)]\n- If $(x_n)$ is increasing and is not bounded above, then\n $x_n\\to+\\infty$.\n- If $(x_n)$ is decreasing and is not bounded below, then\n $x_n\\to-\\infty$.",
